column4: EU regulators to rule on $16.7 billion Intel  Altera deal by October 14
column5: BRUSSELS European Union antitrust regulators will decide by Oct. 14 whether to clear U.S. chipmaker Intel's $16.7 billion bid for Altera Corp  its largest ever deal.
